The '''Bothan Diplomatic Corps''' was one of the few [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] government organizations not to be incorporated into the [[Combined Bothan Clans|Bothan Council]] and was, in fact, expanded. The Diplomatic Corp operated as a branch of the Bothan government and held the responsibility of furthering Bothan ideals through diplomacy. Its agents meets with the leaders of other worlds, forged treaties, and represented [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]] in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], to ensure that Bothan ideals were met in any alliance.

